{"tid":172034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同上屆特首選舉比，今年都幾平淡","createTime":"2017-03-25T16:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T17:04:01.000Z","uid":52195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc205dd0ab14f41c247d90832e1bff7660f3619","tid":172034,"uid":52195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T16:15:03.000Z","msg":"仲記得上年選舉劇情峰迴路轉，唐唐同689互爆，日日都有新玩法。有日記者開晒吊車影唐唐間屋嗰日真係經典。<br />\n今屆完全平淡，聽日就選，跟晒劇本走，結果應該都唔會有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f0598be938cc81c8b1d83907f9babfe48abccd","tid":172034,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"今年可以日日開post屌人係港豬喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就不知幾忙啦<br />\n撐林鄭又港豬<br />\n撐薯片又港豬<br />\n撐胡官因為冇票又港豬<br />\n話不如投白票又係港豬<br />\n唔理又港豬<br />\n好多嘢要屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你就冇嘢做啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947741e302d1025cc42634a270b4d5d05b814144","tid":172034,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T16:32:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"632f787364b4ad6bee143f1726adfe8f3e25a8bd","tid":172034,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"677863cabc8157003c5439e309c61e8756d50e80","tid":172034,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T17:04:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港豬出名政治冷感</blockquote><br />\n政治冷感先唔港豬呀<br />\n知道有件事唔做嘢又係港豬<br />\n做咗，唔激進又係港豬<br />\n激進又話信香港人會幫手係蠢係港豬<br />\n所以政治冷感，得閒又串下人係港豬，不知幾脫俗冇得輸呀"}]}